Symbol.Script_3D:
sectWidth=sectWidth/1000 sectDepth=sectDepth/1000 sectThick=sectThick/1000 flangeThick=flangeThick/1000 Rad=Rad/1000
pen gs_cont_pen material col_mat if gs_shadow=0 then shadow off else shadow on endif
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN end
!---------Cutplanes modz = zzyzx IF bCutPlanes Then
wsds = sqr(sectDepth^2 + sectWidth^2)
!!!-------------------- Top Cutting If ABS(gs_cutang1_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang2_bot) > EPS Then modz = modz+tan(60)* wsds/2
Rotz gs_cutdir_top addz zzyzx rotx 90
cutpoly 5, -wsds/2,tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2,tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang1_bot)* wsds /2, 0,0, -wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang2_bot)* wsds /2
del 3 Endif
!!!-------------------- Bottom Cutting If ABS(gs_cutang3_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang4_bot) > EPS Then modz = modz+tan(60)* wsds /2
Rotz gs_cutdir_but rotx 90
cutpoly 5, -wsds/2,-tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2,-tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang3_bot)* wsds /2, 0,0, -wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang4_bot)* wsds /2
del 2 addz -tan(60)*wsds/2 Endif Endif !---------Cutplanes
RRadius=sectThick*2
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN
PRISM_ 9,modz, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 15, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 15, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 15, sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 15, sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 15, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 15, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 15, -sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 15, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, -1
ENDIF IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN RESOL gs_resol
PRISM_ 15,modz, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 15, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 15, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 15, sectThick/2+Rad, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 79, sectThick/2+Rad, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick+Rad, 979, 0,-90,4079, sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick+Rad, 15, sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 15, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 15, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 15, -sectThick/2-Rad, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 79, -sectThick/2-Rad, sectDepth/2-flangeThick-Rad, 979, 0,-90,4079, -sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick-Rad, 79, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, -1 ENDIF
!---------Cutplanes IF bCutPlanes Then If ABS(gs_cutang1_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang2_bot) > EPS Then cutend
If ABS(gs_cutang3_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang4_bot) > EPS Then del 1 cutend Endif Endif !---------Cutplanes
fullSectWidth = 2*sectWidth-sectThick unID=1 HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1
!---------Bottom Hotspots cutAngleHSBot1 = gs_cutang3_bot cutAngleHSBot3 = gs_cutang4_bot
if iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_X then HPBotx = sectDepth HPxMiddle = sectDepth cutAngleHSBot2 = gs_cutang4_bot cutAngleHSBot4 = gs_cutang3_bot else HPBotx = fullSectWidth HPxMiddle = sectThick cutAngleHSBot2 = gs_cutang3_bot cutAngleHSBot4 = gs_cutang4_bot endif
rotx 90
HOTSPOT fullSectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot2)* HPBotx/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot3)* HPxMiddle/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -fullSectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot4)* HPBotx/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot1)* HPxMiddle/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 del 1
!---------Top Hotspots cutAngleHS1 = gs_cutang1_bot cutAngleHS3 = gs_cutang2_bot
if iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_X then HPx = sectDepth HPxMiddle = sectDepth cutAngleHS2 = gs_cutang2_bot cutAngleHS4 = gs_cutang1_bot else HPx = fullSectWidth HPxMiddle = sectThick cutAngleHS2 = gs_cutang1_bot cutAngleHS4 = gs_cutang2_bot endif
addz zzyzx rotx 90
HOTSPOT fullSectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS2)* HPx/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS3)* HPxMiddle/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -fullSectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS4)* HPx/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS1)* HPxMiddle/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 del 2
end
Symbol.Script_2D:
sectWidth=sectWidth/1000 sectDepth=sectDepth/1000 sectThick=sectThick/1000 flangeThick=flangeThick/1000 Rad=Rad/1000
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
unID=1 hLineID = 1000
HOTSPOT2 0, 0,unID : unID=unID+1
IF axis=1 AND only_axis=0 OR axis=0 THEN
RRadius=sectThick*2
HOTSPOT2 sectWidth-sectThick/2, -b/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -sectWidth+sectThick/2, b/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 sectThick/2, sectDepth/2,unID : unID=unID+1
IF gs_ShowMoreHtps2D=1 THEN HOTSPOT2 sectWidth-sectThick/2, -b/2+flangeThick,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -sectWidth+sectThick/2, b/2-flangeThick,unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_2D_m = 1 THEN
POLY2_b 9, 1+2+4+32, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 1+32, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 1+32, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 1+32, sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 1+32, sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 1+32, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 1+32, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 1+32, -sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 1+32, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, -1
HOTLINE2 0,-sectDepth/2,0,sectDepth/2, hLineID
IF gs_ShowMoreHtps2D=1 THEN HOTSPOT2 sectThick/2, -b/2+flangeThick,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -sectThick/2, b/2-flangeThick,unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
ENDIF IF gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 THEN
POLY2_b 15, 1+2+4+32, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 1+32, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 1+32, sectWidth-sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 1+32, sectThick/2+Rad, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick, 1+32, sectThick/2+Rad, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick+Rad, 901+32, 0,-90,4001+32, sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+flangeThick+Rad, 1+32, sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 1+32, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 1+32, -sectWidth+sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 1+32, -sectThick/2-Rad, sectDepth/2-flangeThick, 1+32, -sectThick/2-Rad, sectDepth/2-flangeThick-Rad, 901+32, 0,-90,4001+32, -sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-flangeThick-Rad, 1+32, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, -1
HOTLINE2 0,-sectDepth/2,0,sectDepth/2, hLineID
IF gs_ShowMoreHtps2D=1 THEN HOTSPOT2 sectThick/2+Rad, -b/2+flangeThick,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 sectThick/2, -b/2+flangeThick+Rad,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 -sectThick/2-Rad, b/2-flangeThick,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -sectThick/2, b/2-flangeThick-Rad,unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
unID=100 IF (axis=1) THEN PEN axis_line_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type
LINE2 -axis_XDim, 0, axis_XDim,0 LINE2 0, -axis_YDim, 0,axis_YDim
FOR k1=1 TO 2 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, axis_XDim, 1+128: unID=unID+1 !!! Axis X Dim. from Origo HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, axis_XDim, 3: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 axis_XDim, 0, unID, axis_XDim, 2: unID=unID+1 ROT2 180 NEXT k1 DEL 2
FOR k2=1 TO 2 ROT2 90 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, axis_YDim, 1+128: unID=unID+1 !!! Axis Y Dim. from Origo HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, axis_YDim, 3: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 axis_YDim, 0, unID, axis_YDim, 2: unID=unID+1 DEL 1 ROT2 180 NEXT k2 DEL 2
IF only_axis=1 THEN HOTSPOT2 0, -sectDepth/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, sectDepth/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 sectWidth-sectThick/2, 0,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -sectWidth+sectThick/2, 0,unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
ENDIF
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001 iStructureCode = 52 !CODECOL_Z
! iCutModeColBottom, iCutModeColTop CUTMODE_ALONG_X = 1 CUTMODE_ALONG_Y = 2
Symbol.Script_VL:
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! hide All Parameters list ! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
sor = 10 ! Number of Sections
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "Profile" or siz_mtr[1] = "" then dim vekt[] for i = sor to 1 step -1 vekt[i] = "" next i
szelv = open("text", "Z Data(14).txt", "separator='\t', mode=ro, Library") for i = 2 to sor+1 n = input(szelv, i, 2, vekt[i-1]) next i
vekt[sor] = `СПЕЦИАЛЬНЫЙ` siz_mtr = vekt
parameters siz_mtr = siz_mtr
close szelv endif file_dependence "Z Data(14).txt" call "FM_types" parameters all
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=28 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19 IF axis_line_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS axis_line_pen=68
VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,) IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN LOCK "gs_resol"
dim stDetLevel3d[3] stDetLevel3d[1] = `Простой` stDetLevel3d[2] = `Детальный` stDetLevel3d[3] = `Откл.`
values "gs_detlevel_3D" stDetLevel3d values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 1, 2, 0
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[2] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[3] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[1] if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[2] if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[3] parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif dim stDetLevel2d[2] stDetLevel2d[1] = `Простой` stDetLevel2d[2] = `Детальный`
values "gs_detlevel_2D" stDetLevel2d values "gs_detlevel_2D_m" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_2D" then gs_detlevel_2D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_2D = stDetLevel2d[2] then gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m else gs_detlevel_2D = stDetLevel2d[1] if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_2D = stDetLevel2d[2] parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D endif
!---------Cutplanes dim stCutModeColValues[2] stCutModeColValues[1] = `Вдоль оси X` stCutModeColValues[2] = `Вдоль оси Y`
values "stCutModeColTop" stCutModeColValues values "iCutModeColTop" CUTMODE_ALONG_X, CUTMODE_ALONG_Y
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stCutModeColTop" then iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_X if stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColValues[2] then iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y parameters iCutModeColTop = iCutModeColTop else stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColValues[1] if iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y then stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColValues[2] parameters stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColTop endif
values "stCutModeColBottom" stCutModeColValues values "iCutModeColBottom" CUTMODE_ALONG_X, CUTMODE_ALONG_Y
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stCutModeColBottom" then iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_X if stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColValues[2] then iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y parameters iCutModeColBottom = iCutModeColBottom else stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColValues[1] if iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y then stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColValues[2] parameters stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColBottom endif values "gs_cutdir_top" RANGE [-90,90] values "gs_cutdir_but" RANGE [-90,90] values "gs_cutang1_bot" RANGE [-60,60] values "gs_cutang2_bot" RANGE [-60,60] values "gs_cutang3_bot" RANGE [-60,60] values "gs_cutang4_bot" RANGE [-60,60]
IF iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y Then parameters gs_cutdir_top = 0.00 gs_cutdir_top = 0.00 Else parameters gs_cutdir_top = 90.00 gs_cutdir_top = 90.00 Endif
IF iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y Then parameters gs_cutdir_but = 0.00 gs_cutdir_but = 0.00 Else parameters gs_cutdir_but = 90.00 gs_cutdir_but = 90.00 Endif
IF NOT(bCutPlanes) Then hideparameter "stCutModeColTop", "iCutModeColTop", "stCutModeColBottom", "iCutModeColBottom", "gs_cutang1_bot","gs_cutang2_bot","gs_cutang3_bot","gs_cutang4_bot" Lock "stCutModeColTop", "iCutModeColTop", "stCutModeColBottom", "iCutModeColBottom", "gs_cutang1_bot","gs_cutang2_bot","gs_cutang3_bot","gs_cutang4_bot" Endif !---------Cutplanes
values "Profile" siz_mtr
if Profile<>`СПЕЦИАЛЬНЫЙ` & Profile <> lastProfile then
lastProfile = Profile parameters lastProfile = Profile
szelv=open("text", "Z Data(14).txt", "separator='\t', mode=ro, Library") for i=2 to sor+1 n=input(szelv, i, 2, ker) if Profile=ker then n=input(szelv, i, 3, osectDepth, osectWidth, osectThick, oflangeThick, osectArea, omassPerMeter, oAngle, osecondMomentX, oelastModX, \ ogyrationRadX, osecondMomentY, oelastModY, ogyrationRadY, osecondMomentS, oelastModS, ogyrationRadS, osecondMomentN, oelastModN, ogyrationRadN, otc) i=sor+1 ! force loop end endif next i close szelv
parameters a=2*osectWidth/1000-osectThick/1000 a=2*osectWidth/1000-osectThick/1000 parameters b=osectDepth/1000 b=osectDepth/1000 parameters massPerMeter=omassPerMeter massPerMeter=omassPerMeter parameters sectDepth=osectDepth sectDepth=osectDepth parameters sectWidth=osectWidth sectWidth=osectWidth parameters sectThick=osectThick sectThick=osectThick parameters flangeThick=oflangeThick flangeThick=oflangeThick parameters Rad=flangeThick Rad=flangeThick parameters Angle=oAngle Angle=oAngle parameters secondMomentX=osecondMomentX secondMomentX=osecondMomentX parameters secondMomentY=osecondMomentY secondMomentY=osecondMomentY parameters secondMomentS=osecondMomentS secondMomentS=osecondMomentS parameters secondMomentN=osecondMomentN secondMomentN=osecondMomentN parameters gyrationRadX=ogyrationRadX gyrationRadX=ogyrationRadX parameters gyrationRadY=ogyrationRadY gyrationRadY=ogyrationRadY parameters gyrationRadS=ogyrationRadS gyrationRadS=ogyrationRadS parameters gyrationRadN=ogyrationRadN gyrationRadN=ogyrationRadN parameters elastModX=oelastModX elastModX=oelastModX parameters elastModY=oelastModY elastModY=oelastModY parameters elastModS=oelastModS elastModS=oelastModS parameters elastModN=oelastModN elastModN=oelastModN parameters sectArea=osectArea sectArea=osectArea endif
if Profile<>`СПЕЦИАЛЬНЫЙ` then
lock "a" lock "b" lock "massPerMeter" lock "sectDepth" lock "sectWidth" lock "sectThick" lock "flangeThick" lock "Rad" lock "Angle" lock "secondMomentX" lock "secondMomentY" lock "secondMomentS" lock "secondMomentN" lock "gyrationRadX" lock "gyrationRadY" lock "gyrationRadS" lock "gyrationRadN" lock "elastModX" lock "elastModY" lock "elastModS" lock "elastModN" lock "sectArea" else values "flangeThick" range (0, ) values "sectThick" range (0, ) values "sectWidth" range (sectThick, ) values "sectDepth" range (2*flangeThick, ) values "Rad" range [0, min(sectWidth-sectThick, sectDepth-flangeThick)]
parameters massPerMeter=massPerMeter parameters sectDepth=sectDepth parameters sectWidth=sectWidth parameters sectThick=sectThick parameters flangeThick=flangeThick parameters Rad=Rad parameters secondMomentX=secondMomentX parameters secondMomentY=secondMomentY parameters secondMomentS=secondMomentS parameters secondMomentN=secondMomentN parameters gyrationRadX=gyrationRadX parameters gyrationRadY=gyrationRadY parameters gyrationRadS=gyrationRadS parameters gyrationRadN=gyrationRadN parameters elastModX=elastModX parameters elastModY=elastModY parameters elastModS=elastModS parameters elastModN=elastModN parameters sectArea=sectArea if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then sectWidth = (A+sectThick/1000)*1000/2 parameters sectWidth = sectWidth else A = 2*sectWidth/1000-sectThick/1000 parameters A = A endif if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "sectDepth" then B = sectDepth/1000 parameters B = B else sectDepth = B*1000 parameters sectDepth = sectDepth endif endif
massSum=massPerMeter*ZZYZX parameters massSum=massSum lock "massSum"
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME="Profile" THEN axis_XDim=a/2+0.05 PARAMETERS axis_XDim = axis_XDim
axis_YDim=b/2+0.05 PARAMETERS axis_YDim = axis_YDim ENDIF
if not(axis) then lock "only_axis", "axis_line_type", "axis_line_pen", "axis_XDim", "axis_YDim" endif if axis and only_axis then lock "gs_cont_pen", "gs_fill_type", "gs_fill_pen", "gs_back_pen", "gs_detlevel_2D", "gs_ShowMoreHtps2D" endif
parameters ac_bottomlevel = 0 parameters ac_toplevel = ZZYZX

dim stPropParamNames[16] stPropParamNames[1] = "secondMomentX" stPropParamNames[2] = "secondMomentY" stPropParamNames[3] = "gyrationRadX" stPropParamNames[4] = "gyrationRadY" stPropParamNames[5] = "elastModX" stPropParamNames[6] = "elastModY" stPropParamNames[7] = "Angle"
stPropParamNames[8] = "secondMomentS" stPropParamNames[9] = "secondMomentN" stPropParamNames[10] = "gyrationRadS" stPropParamNames[11] = "gyrationRadN" stPropParamNames[12] = "elastModS" stPropParamNames[13] = "elastModN" stPropParamNames[14] = "sectArea" stPropParamNames[15] = "massPerMeter" stPropParamNames[16] = "massSum"
